data.title: Zulfikar Ali Bhutto: No place for me in Pakistani politics – DW – 08
data.meta_description: Zulfikar Ali Bhutto Jr tells DW why he didn't continue the political legacy of the Bhutto dynasty. Identifying as a Pakistani Muslim artist, he says he focuses on Sindh province's indigenous craftwork, wildlife advocacy and climate justice.
data.text:
08/16/2022August 16, 2022

Zulfikar Ali Bhutto Jr tells DW why he didn't continue the political legacy of the Bhutto dynasty. Identifying as a Pakistani Muslim artist, he says he focuses on Sindh province's indigenous craftwork, wildlife advocacy and climate justice.
